z = (p-o)'S'S(p-o) dz/dp = 2S'S(p-o)

z = (s*(px-ox))^2 + (s*(py-oy))^2 dz/dox = -2(s*(px-ox))*s dz/ds = 2*s*[(px-ox)^2 + (py-oy)^2]

z = (s*dx)^2 + (s*dy)^2 dz/ds = 2(s*dx)*dx + 2(s*dy)*dy
